'''''Senatorial Record Digest''''' was a publication sent out by the [[Imperial Senate/Legends|Senate]] [[Cam droid/Legends|cam droids]] to the personal [[Computer/Legends|computers]] of [[Senator/Legends|senators]]. The transcript summarized the hourly events of the day. It was also available as a [[Durasheet/Legends|durasheet]] hardcopy sold on the streets of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

==Appearances==
